title: EMC ScaleIO: Storage Pool Total read/write
agents: linux
catalog: os/storage
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check measures the total r/w of a Storage Pool (SP). The ruleset
 "Levels for disk IO" can be used to set thresholds for read/write throughput.

item:
 The SP id is used as item

inventory:
 One service for each SP is created
